'{"questions":[{"questionID":19,"question_content":"How is your inburgering going so far? Where do you feel pressure in your life, with the inburgering? What feels difficult to handle?","main_indicator":"education","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":20,"question_content":"Do you work? If yes: is your work paid, or volunteer work?","main_indicator":"work","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":21,"question_content":"How do you feel about your work/volunteer work/not having work?","main_indicator":"work","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":22,"question_content":"At the point you are currently in (within the inburgering), do you feel like you want to be working? Is there space in your life to combine work/volunteer work with other responsibilities? Why yes/why not?","main_indicator":"work","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":23,"question_content":"If you are working/doing volunteer work: Do you feel like your work/volunteer work fits with your skills, interests and needs? Why yes/why not?","main_indicator":"work","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":24,"question_content":"For everyone in the group: What is missing for you when it comes to work/volunteer work? What do you need to feel happier?","main_indicator":"work","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":25,"question_content":"For everyone in the group: What blocks you from getting there [to what is missing/would make you happier]?","main_indicator":"work","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":26,"question_content":"What’s one thing the municipality can do to make it easier for you to get there?","main_indicator":"work","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":27,"question_content":"Warm up: How often do you feel people are around you, vs how often do you feel people are ‘with’ you?","main_indicator":"bridges","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":28,"question_content":"What makes it difficult to meet new people?","main_indicator":"bridges","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":29,"question_content":"Do you actively try to meet new people? Why yes/why not?","main_indicator":"bridges","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":30,"question_content":"If yes: Where do you try to meet new people? In what ways do you try to meet new people?","main_indicator":"bridges","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":31,"question_content":"If no: what stops you from trying?","main_indicator":"bridges","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":32,"question_content":"When you look at your social connections now, who is missing? What kind of contacts and relationships do you want to have more of?","main_indicator":"bridges","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":33,"question_content":"What’s one thing that the municipality can do to make it easier for you to meet new people?","main_indicator":"bridges","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":34,"question_content":"From the survey, we have seen that many people want to improve their Dutch by practicing it with other people. In what ways would you like that to be set-up? What can the municipality do to facilitate this practice?","main_indicator":"language","followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":35,"question_content":"Is there anything that we didn’t discuss in this session, that you feel is important to add?","main_indicator":null,"followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null},{"questionID":36,"question_content":"Anything that is big and affects your life and needs attention from the municipality?","main_indicator":null,"followed_questionID":null,"following_trigger":null}]}'
'{"answers":[{"answerID":90,"questionID":19,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"There is a gap in communication between the school and the municipality. We tried several times to submit a complaint about the school, but the municipality did not respond. Once, I suspected that the school translated a problem and a complaint about itself to the municipality, and I later discovered that the translation was not accurate. My relationship with the school lacks trust, and we became afraid that the school might deliver our message in a negative way. That is why I am happy today that there is an external third party.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":91,"questionID":19,"participantID":13,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Integration is generally not beneficial. The school does not help me; I study by myself. Artificial intelligence has helped me more than the school. The number of study hours for the B1 level is not appropriate, and the training system is also unsuitable. The exams make me feel pressured, and I discovered that the school did not support me well or prepare me properly for the exams, which caused me great stress.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":92,"questionID":19,"participantID":14,"answer_content_oriLAN":"My municipality is good (Gemert). The school is good, and communication with the municipality is good. I am under pressure from Senzer, especially regarding work, and I cannot find suitable employment, which worries me. They do not help me but put more pressure on me.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":93,"questionID":19,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I feel that the study curriculum has shortcomings and that the education system is slow and not suitable for the Dutch labor market. In practical life, I do not fully benefit from the school curriculum and do not see it reflected in my working life. For example, they give us computers but do not provide training on how to use them. I feel pressure regarding my children’s education, and I do not feel that the municipality helped me by providing a clear program to understand the general system, such as taxes, education, and other issues.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":94,"questionID":19,"participantID":16,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Integration in general is good. I was delayed for a long time before I started integration, and when I did start, I felt that the municipality was pressuring me, and overall I am not comfortable.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":95,"questionID":19,"participantID":17,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Integration is generally good for me, but there was a delay in education. Communication with the municipality is generally bad. After several months, I started to feel more comfortable. I feel pressure from voluntary work and studying. For example, I was late in entering school and starting integration; I stayed at home for a full year until I was accepted into the integration program. Voluntary work is generally good","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":96,"questionID":22,"participantID":13,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Yes. I already have paid work as a kitchen assistant, and I like this type of work.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":97,"questionID":22,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I do voluntary work as a cook two days per week.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":98,"questionID":22,"participantID":14,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I do voluntary work in a warehouse company. I have finished my required voluntary hours but continue working.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":99,"questionID":22,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Yes. I have paid work now. I work in a meat company after finishing my voluntary work.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":100,"questionID":22,"participantID":16,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I do voluntary work in gardening.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":101,"questionID":22,"participantID":17,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I have part-time paid work in cleaning and I also do voluntary work.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":102,"questionID":22,"participantID":13,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Yes. I was able to combine work with my responsibilities and did not feel pressured. When I faced problems at work, Senzer helped me.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":103,"questionID":22,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"No. I have health issues, six children, school, and voluntary work at the same time. The responsibilities are too heavy, and the municipality did not cooperate with me to get an exemption.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":104,"questionID":22,"participantID":14,"answer_content_oriLAN":"It is difficult because of my health condition. I asked for adjustments, but they did not cooperate properly, and I feel tired now.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":105,"questionID":22,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"It is very stressful to combine paid work with integration, especially because I have family responsibilities and my wife has health issues.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":106,"questionID":22,"participantID":16,"answer_content_oriLAN":"It is manageable, but the work is physically tiring.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":107,"questionID":22,"participantID":17,"answer_content_oriLAN":"It is difficult. I only accepted the paid job to reduce pressure from Senzer.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":108,"questionID":23,"participantID":13,"answer_content_oriLAN":"My current job is relatively suitable, and I enjoy it, but my previous education and work experience were not taken into account.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":109,"questionID":23,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I like cooking, but the voluntary work is exhausting, limits my development, and does not help me improve my language. I also experience discrimination.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":110,"questionID":23,"participantID":14,"answer_content_oriLAN":"No. Most workers are Arabic speakers, so it does not help me learn Dutch or integrate.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":111,"questionID":23,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"No. My experience is in sewing, and the current job in a meat company is completely unrelated.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":112,"questionID":23,"participantID":16,"answer_content_oriLAN":"No. Voluntary work in gardening does not suit me. I want to work in buying and selling.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":113,"questionID":23,"participantID":17,"answer_content_oriLAN":"No. Cleaning work is not suitable for me and is far from where I live.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":114,"questionID":24,"participantID":13,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Access to vocational education. I want to study fashion design, but the municipality did not help me.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":115,"questionID":24,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Flexibility regarding my health situation, understanding of my family responsibilities, and motivating work.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":116,"questionID":24,"participantID":14,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Suitable, lighter work and proper language support.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":117,"questionID":24,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Support to find work or vocational training in sewing or carpentry.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":118,"questionID":24,"participantID":16,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Contact with Dutch society and opportunities in the field I want to work in.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":119,"questionID":24,"participantID":17,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Work in my own field (car mechanics) and more integration hours to finish faster.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":120,"questionID":25,"participantID":13,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Lack of support from the municipality for vocational training.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":121,"questionID":25,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Health issues, heavy responsibilities, lack of municipal cooperation, and discrimination.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":122,"questionID":25,"participantID":14,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Health problems, language barriers, and lack of municipal support.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":123,"questionID":25,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Pressure from Senzer and lack of municipal support, forcing me into unsuitable work.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":124,"questionID":25,"participantID":16,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Lack of guidance, no meetings with Senzer or the municipality, and no real evaluation.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":125,"questionID":25,"participantID":17,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Lack of language skills and lack of municipal support to work in my field.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":126,"questionID":26,"participantID":13,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Support access to vocational education and take my previous experience into account.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":127,"questionID":26,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Provide exemptions or adjustments based on health conditions and family responsibilities.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":128,"questionID":26,"participantID":14,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Help me find suitable, non-physically demanding work and support my language learning.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":129,"questionID":26,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Help me find work or vocational training in sewing or carpentry instead of pressuring me.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":130,"questionID":26,"participantID":16,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Help me connect more with Dutch society and arrange voluntary work in shops or trade-related places.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":131,"questionID":26,"participantID":17,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Increase integration hours so I can finish faster and help me find work (paid or voluntary) in my own field instead of unrelated jobs.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":132,"questionID":29,"participantID":18,"answer_content_oriLAN":"The biggest obstacles are language and cultural differences. I have a Dutch neighbor who is one of my closest friends. I try to meet new people mainly at work, but my current job does not help me. I also go to the local café, but it is difficult to build relationships there.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":133,"questionID":29,"participantID":19,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Language and acceptance from the local community are the main obstacles. I feel isolated in my neighborhood. I try to meet Dutch people in public spaces, parks, shops, or the neighborhood, but they are not welcoming. Voluntary work is mostly Syrians, which also limits interaction with Dutch people.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":134,"questionID":29,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"My contact with the local community is generally good. A volunteer at the taal coach program helps me with daily life and my children. My neighbors are supportive, and we exchange gifts and help each other.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":135,"questionID":29,"participantID":20,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I try to network with neighbors, invite them to eat or distribute food. I participate in municipal activities and celebrations to feel part of the community.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":136,"questionID":29,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Language is the main obstacle. I try to meet new people mainly through cooking, sharing meals, and going to the park with my children. Some people are welcoming, others are not.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":137,"questionID":29,"participantID":13,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I started trying to get to know Dutch society. Language and cultural differences are obstacles. I participate in voluntary work, such as at a hospital, which helps me meet people.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":138,"questionID":29,"participantID":21,"answer_content_oriLAN":"I don’t have Dutch friends because I don’t speak Dutch well. I try to meet people through voluntary work and at my workplace, but Dutch colleagues and customers are not very open.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":139,"questionID":30,"participantID":18,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Through work, cafés, and sharing cultural practices like cooking. I also tried organizing collective events during Ramadan, but neighbors were hesitant.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":140,"questionID":30,"participantID":19,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Through public spaces like parks and shops, and by offering services or help to neighbors, though they are not receptive.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":141,"questionID":30,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Through municipal activities, school, and exchanging small favors or gifts with neighbors.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":142,"questionID":30,"participantID":20,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Through neighborhood networking, municipal activities, games, and celebrations. WhatsApp groups help maintain contact.","date":null,"data_source_ca