36,"participantID":16,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Social isolation and the lack of welcoming spaces in the neighborhood are big issues that need municipal attention.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":155,"questionID":36,"participantID":15,"answer_content_oriLAN":"The municipality could help with opportunities to combine integration, language learning, and work/training aligned with my skills.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":156,"questionID":36,"participantID":14,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Lack of relatives and the difficulty of integrating into Dutch social networks are major issues. Language support is essential.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":157,"questionID":36,"participantID":12,"answer_content_oriLAN":"Health limitations, family responsibilities, and the inflexibility of the integration system create stress and need attention from the municipality.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"},{"answerID":158,"questionID":36,"participantID":22,"answer_content_oriLAN":"The difference between the school curriculum and practical work life is a major issue. More vocational support is needed.","date":null,"data_source_category":"expertpool","data_source":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1c2mluOxn_TMZsoHD52_0WW4pkLMbe-1wjaApJA1rpPA/edit?tab=t.0"}]}'